---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Bambi â€” Lina" bgColor="#F5F5F0">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-14">

    <!-- Header image -->
    <img src="/bambi/IMG_0518.jpeg" alt="Bambi" class="w-full mb-10" />

    <!-- Title -->
    <h1 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900" style="font-size: 32px;">Bambi</h1>

    <!-- Story Background -->
    <section class="mt-6 mb-10">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3" style="font-size: 20px;">Story Background:</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">
        Our story starts with a little girl (Rim) who always wanted to have a cat. But her grandmother is allergic to cats. To her surprise, on a sunny morning, her Teta knits her a black cat. Rim is feeling above the clouds due to her new knitted cat. She named it 'Bambi'. At night, Bambi starts moving. It is alive! The two go on great daily adventures and become the best of friends, until something terrible happens.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Progress -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3" style="font-size: 20px;">Progress:</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-6">
        The story and sketches are still in progress. The sketches were all drawn in photoshop.
      </p>

      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">
        Page 1 kicks off our story with Teta Sausan, who is practicing their favourite hobby of all times, knitting.
      </p>
      <img src="/bambi/bambi-1.jpeg" alt="Teta Sausan knitting" class="w-full mb-6" />

      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">
        Rim and Bambi sitting on the Balcony eating 'Manakish' looking at the street.
      </p>
      <img src="/bambi/bambi-2.jpeg" alt="Rim and Bambi on the balcony" class="w-full mb-6" />

      <img src="/bambi/bambi-4.jpeg" alt="Bambi illustration" class="w-full mb-6" />

      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">
        Rim and Bambi exploring the holes around the village, will they find anything interesting?
      </p>
      <img src="/bambi/bambi-6.jpeg" alt="Rim and Bambi exploring" class="w-full mb-6" />

      <img src="/bambi/bambi-7.jpeg" alt="Bambi illustration" class="w-full mb-6" />

      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">
        Rim and Bambi playing 'Ghomida', aka hide and seek.
      </p>
      <img src="/bambi/bambi-9.jpeg" alt="Rim and Bambi playing hide and seek" class="w-full mb-6" />
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
